{"tid":2494010,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人答到我內射同中出嘅分別係咩？","createTime":"2021-04-18T10:40:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T11:50:37.000Z","uid":376713,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"db7103c61a8368340c19b416fa17cc16a3950c1e","tid":2494010,"uid":376713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:40:06.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a731af8cd1a1cc67e21f816f67dae24064e15ff0","tid":2494010,"uid":314072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:40:41.000Z","msg":"無"},{"pid":"8f97c9532630ecca1ca6b12258c8fe960a11e78c","tid":2494010,"uid":24570,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:41:43.000Z","msg":"內射：戴住套<br />\n中出：冇戴套"},{"pid":"9831a663315b2bb68b3ce302a0a1f1d925c7ad9d","tid":2494010,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8f97c9532630ecca1ca6b12258c8fe960a11e78c","tid":2494010,"uid":24570,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:41:43.000Z","msg":"內射：戴住套<br />\n中出：冇戴套"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:42:39.000Z","msg":"體內射精簡稱內射，俗稱中出，是指人類男性在達到性高潮時於性伴侶之陰道或直腸中射精的情況，通常在沒有戴上保險套的陰道性交或肛交中發生。在女性陰道內的體內射精是引發體內受精並使之懷孕的主要方式。而由於能夠導致懷孕以及能夠透過精液傳遞性傳染疾病，體內射精被視為一種不安全性行為。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%AB%94%E5%85%A7%E5%B0%84%E7%B2%BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%25B2%25BE&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVpnpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=3adfb89f\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%AB%94%E5%85%A7%E5%B0%84%E7%B2%BE</a>"},{"pid":"0195062702a55cbf9ceef7fce59c897eeba15cca","tid":2494010,"uid":74778,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f97c9532630ecca1ca6b12258c8fe960a11e78c","tid":2494010,"uid":24570,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:41:43.000Z","msg":"內射：戴住套<br />\n中出：冇戴套"},"citedBy"